reviewText: Great TV show,Locations, Stories, Corvette. (beautiful Frost blue, first couple shows a 60' then a 61) Acting is good,sometimes dramatic, but nonetheless good.(I did not grow up in the 60's and I love the show) love the Vette.

I have season one volume one of route 66 and have enjoyed it.  The season one volume two did not interest me because of the idea of taking a 60's tv show and making it letterbox.  I hope this mistake is remedied in season two volume one.  Why fool or fiddle with a good thing?
